 428:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c **** /**
 429:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @brief  This function configures system clock with MSI as clock source of the PLL
 430:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @note   The application needs to ensure that PLL, PLLSAI1 and/or PLLSAI2 are disabled.
 431:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @note   Function is based on the following formula:
 432:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *         - PLL output frequency = (((MSI frequency / PLLM) * PLLN) / PLLR)
 433:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *         - PLLM: ensure that the VCO input frequency ranges from 4 to 16 MHz (PLLVCO_input = MSI
 434:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *         - PLLN: ensure that the VCO output frequency is between 64 and 344 MHz (PLLVCO_output =
 435:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *         - PLLR: ensure that max frequency at 120000000 Hz is reached (PLLVCO_output / PLLR)
 436:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @param  UTILS_PLLInitStruct pointer to a @ref LL_UTILS_PLLInitTypeDef structure that contains
 437:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *                             the configuration information for the PLL.
 438:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @param  UTILS_ClkInitStruct pointer to a @ref LL_UTILS_ClkInitTypeDef structure that contains
 439:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *                             the configuration information for the BUS prescalers.
 440:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   * @retval An ErrorStatus enumeration value:
 441:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *          - SUCCESS: Max frequency configuration done
 442:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   *          - ERROR: Max frequency configuration not done
 443:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_utils.c ****   */
